reviewText: This DVD is just OK. First of all, Paul's voice is horrible. Definitely no autotune this show. Also, they cut out things, like Genes bass solo, Paul's banter, and some other parts. So over all, just OK

This is a very good concert except in the beginning they don't show how the curtain goes down (little detail for the cameramen), just for real fans, same as all the ones, the end is not spectacular as usual.
